│   │  covers: C5568443, C5688901, C0188146
│   ├── ✔ C5568443  Arthroplasty of knee planned            IC=14.8
│   ├── ✔ C5688901  Arthroplasty using robotic assist       IC=14.8
│   └── ✔ C0188146  Arthroplasty of knee, tibial plateau    IC=14.8
