Convergence selection (highest IC first):
  Prosthesis of knee (IC=10.2) → 2 CUIs → Subtopic A
  Arthroplasty of knee joint (IC=9.7) → 3 CUIs → Subtopic B
  Operation on knee (IC=6.4) → REJECTED (below floor)

Topic grouper: ancestor of both subtopics
→ 1 topic, 2 subtopics, 5 member CUIs

